{"000-section": {"000-title": "PM Awas Yojana (Urban) Guidelines Updated for BLC", "001-normal": "There are 3 more components under the [PM Awas Yojana](https://sarkariyojana.com/pradhan-mantri-awas-yojana-pmay/) giving more options to beneficiaries, three more components are In-situ Slum Redevelopment, Affordable Housing in Partnership and Credit Linked Subsidy Scheme.", "002-normal": "The central government aims to provide homes to 20 million urban poor by the year 2022 under the mission.", "003-normal": "[Pradhan Mantri Gramin Awas Yojana](https://sarkariyojana.com/pradhan-mantri-awas-yojana-gramin/) has also been launched by the central government to provide houses to the Rural Poor. Under the Gramin Awas Yojana, government will build 3 Crore Pucca houses for rural poor by the year 2022."}}